PURPOSE
  Python script to output the top N most requested DNS lookups
  and clients from a BIND DNS server.

STATUS
  Working as of: 2020-10-14

DETAILS
  This script will count and display the top N most requested
  DNS lookups and clients from a BIND DNS server. Tested on
  Debian.

INSTALL
  01 : Include named.conf.topq in your named.conf file.
  02 : Create the /var/log/bind folder and ensure your BIND
       process has write permissions to it.
  03 : Copy to topq.py /usr/local/sbin and chmod +x. (optionally remove .py extension)
  04 : Use and enjoy.

